      <title>交通谈判陷入僵局，多伦多准备罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/toronto-commuters-brace-for-friday-strike-as-transit-talks-stall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多市政府与工会运输工人之间的劳资谈判在罢工前数小时陷入僵局，此次罢工有可能扰乱加拿大人口最多的城市 150 多万通勤者的生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/toronto-commuters-brace-for-friday-strike-as-transit-talks-stall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Core Scientific 拒绝 10 亿美元收购要约后股价大涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bitcoin-miner-core-rejects-ai-firm-coreweave-s-1-billion-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币矿商 Core Scientific Inc. 拒绝了人工智能初创公司 CoreWeave Inc. 提出的 10 亿美元主动收购要约，就在几天前，两家公司宣布建立合作伙伴关系，预计合作将产生约 35 亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bitcoin-miner-core-rejects-ai-firm-coreweave-s-1-billion-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:51:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
